                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4">
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  Our pricing varies based on the project type and complexity. We offer multiple pricing tiers for each service:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                  <li>Restaurant Menu Systems: Starting from ₹15,000</li>
                  <li>Android TV Apps: Starting from ₹45,000</li>
                  <li>Streaming Mobile Apps: Starting from ₹55,000</li>
