                  <li>Project requirements and specifications</li>
                  <li>Brand guidelines (colors, logos, fonts)</li>
                  <li>Content (text, images, menu items)</li>
                  <li>Preferred features and functionality</li>
                  <li>Any specific design preferences</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
