                  and suggest the best solutions for your business.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 faq-button" data-faq-toggle>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Can I make changes after the project is delivered?</span>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4">
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  Yes! We include 30 days of free revisions after project delivery. During this period, 
                  you can request changes and modifications at no additional cost. After 30 days, we offer 
                  ongoing support and maintenance packages to help you keep your project updated and running smoothly.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 faq-button" data-faq-toggle>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Do you provide ongoing support?</span>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                  </svg>
